      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we've got a massive problem. The press just caught wind that the candidate is changing their stance on the Tax Act compared to what they said last month. If the news starts calling this a \"flip-flop,\" our Consistency Score is going to tank and the polls will bleed. How do we handle the reporter's question about the shift in position? We need to shut down the \"inconsistency\" narrative immediately.",
