      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"evolution\" line sounds a bit too polished. If I push that too hard, the reporter is just going to dig deeper and ask what specific \"new data\" we're talking about, since the candidate hasn't actually released any new studies or reports. Are you sure we shouldn't just be honest and say we've re-evaluated the economic projections? I don't want to get caught in a lie if they start asking for receipts.",
